CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 24, 1957, pg. B7 reads: "Belsaw Cup Winners at the Pittsburgh tournament were John C. Jones, Chicago; Valaria Rinehart, Chicago, Veronica Jackson, Chicago, was the senior master individual. Beulah Jones, Chicago, and Porter Davis were second in pairs Dan Arrindell, New York City, second senior master open pair."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of bridge trophy winners, from left: John C. Jones, Valaria Rinehart, Veronica Jackson, Beulah Jones, Porter Davis, and Dan Arrindell, standing in Fort Pitt Hotel for 24th annual American Bridge Association tournament
